<p>This is the first day of your bootcamp where youâ€™ll be guided through different steps to get you ready to start the
  bootcamp.
  First, choose your character and enter your name.</p>

<div class="select-gender">
  <div class="gender-pick" data-gender="guy"><%= image_tag 'GuyFront' %><p class="select-text">I'm a guy !</p>
  </div>
  <div class="gender-pick" data-gender="girl"><%= image_tag 'GirlFront' %><p class="select-text">I'm a girl !</p>
  </div>
  <div class="gender-pick" data-gender="alien"><%= image_tag 'AlienFront' %><p class="select-text">I'm an alien !</p>
  </div>
